-- Mediobanca says begins arbitrage between Carige shares, cash call rights
-- By Agnieszka Flak
-- Wed Jun 18, 2014 01:55AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, June 18 (Reuters) - Italian investment bank Mediobanca <MDBI.MI> said on Wednesday it had begun to arbitrage between ordinary Banca Carige <CRGI.MI> shares and option rights related to the lender's capital increase.

Mediobanca said the activity could impact up to a maximum of 151 million Banca Carige shares.